Package: ggmultiplot
Title: Reproduce Statistical Plot Styles of 10 Major Graphing Software Packages
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Feng", "Qiao", , "fengq@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: One-stop ggplot2 extension that reproduces the default plot styles
    of 10 major statistical graphing software packages. A single ggchoice() call
    applies the complete visual style (theme + colour/fill scales) for GraphPad
    Prism, SPSS, OriginPro, Stata (s2color), SigmaPlot, JMP, MATLAB, Minitab,
    MedCalc, and classic academic (AMS/Science) output.
